WEBVTT

00:00.539 --> 00:01.338
Tom!

00:01.339 --> 00:04.873
I would like you to redesign
our Parks department logo.

00:04.941 --> 00:06.208
Sounds cool so far.

00:06.776 --> 00:09.878
Rethink our visual brand,
take these words,

00:09.946 --> 00:12.547
and make
something amazing.

00:12.615 --> 00:14.249
So you're saying you want me
to choose a new font?

00:14.317 --> 00:16.617
Yes, essentially I'd like
you to choose a new font.

00:16.684 --> 00:18.185
Jerry, I am making you
my number-two guy

00:18.753 --> 00:19.753
on the new font project.

00:19.821 --> 00:21.989
Come on, that's too close.
Let's make him a number-three.

00:22.057 --> 00:23.357
Fair enough.
Jerry, you're number three.

00:23.425 --> 00:25.293
There's only two of us.

00:25.360 --> 00:28.529
He has been
in this department a long time.

00:28.596 --> 00:30.131
I think maybe you could
learn somethg from him.

